**Example 1: 创建Notebook授权Url**



Input: 

```
tccli tione CreatePresignedNotebookInstanceUrl --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --NotebookInstanceName test \
    --SessionExpirationDurationInSeconds 1800
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "RequestId": "1f0a0715-e1d9-41a6-b511-729f96b97810",
        "AuthorizedUrl": "https://test.notebook.ap-guangzhou.ti.tencentcs.com/auth?authToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..wIUFsHrhNhysizMtabH74bTqpKJmx5XeoxIily0JRWs&view=lab"
    }
}
```
